parameters:
One-armed Opro: '...Is this all? It doesn't compare to the
threat of the Ogre.'

One-armed Opro: I'm glad you're safe. I've heard that a
dragon has appeared.
Mage Relm: Um, Opro-san, can you use magic?

Mage Relm: I can feel tremendous magical power emanating
from the greatsword. It feels different from the magic we
use.

One-armed Opro: Perhaps... those [people] in that ruins
might have done something.

One-armed Opro: It seems like I've become quite popular
among the greatswords before coming here.

Mage Relm: Opro-san, please come with us! The dragon is
like a manifestation of magical power.

Mage Relm: With that greatsword, you can definitely cut
through the dragon!
One-armed Opro: That's exciting... Do you mind, Clea?
Clea: Of course, let's defeat the dragon together.

One-armed Opro: Together, let's defeat the dragon... I'm
glad to hear those words from you all.

\CL Relm has acquired the support skill Evil Slash \C[0]
and can now use it \|.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Thief Nora (I smell a familiar scent... I wonder who it
is... There's too much smell of blood to tell though...)

Thief Nora (I smell a familiar scent... It feels like the
scent of someone I know... and it's a very strong scent...)
Thief Nora (I wonder who it is...?)
